<h4 style="color: #DAA520;">Closed Beta: Patch 32.1 (July 17th, 2014)</h4><ul><li><b>Base Stats</b></li><ul><li>Base Health reduced to 525, down from 540.</li><li>Health per level reduced to 78, down from 84.</li></ul><li><b>Passive - Celerity</b></li><ul><li>The Attack Speed bonus granted by this passive ability has been increased to 33-80% (based on level), up from 22-60%.</li></ul></ul><h4 style="color: #DAA520;">Closed Beta: Patch 32 (July 9th, 2014)</h4><ul><li><B>Passive - Celerity</B></li><ul><li>Fixed a bug where Moya was gaining more attack speed than intended under most circumstances.</li></ul></ul><h4 style="color: #DAA520;">Closed Beta: Patch 28 (April 8, 2014)</h4><ul><li><B>Shock (W)</B></li><ul><li>The basic attack damage bonus on this ability has been increased to 15/20/25/30/35, up from 10/15/20/25/30.</li></ul><li><B>Recharge (E)</B></li><ul><li>The basic attack damage bonus on this ability has been increased to 15/20/25/30/35, up from 10/15/20/25/30.</li></ul></ul><h4 style="color: #DAA520;">Closed Beta: Patch 26 (Feb 24, 2014)</h4><ul><li>Celerity (Passive)</li><ul><li>The attack speed gained based on missing energy has been reduced to a maximum value of 22% to 60%, down from 35% to 130% (the value scales with level).</li></ul><li>Bolt (Q)</li><ul><li>The displayed range of this ability has been updated to 400, from previous value of 450.</li></ul><li>Shock (W)</li><ul><li>The basic attack bonus damage of this ability has been reduced to 10/15/20/25/30, down from 15/20/25/30/35.</li><li>The basic attack bonus damage Power ratio has been reduced to 0.1, down from 0.15.</li></ul><li>Recharge (E)</li><ul><li>The basic attack bonus damage of this ability has been reduced to 10/15/20/25/30, down from 15/20/25/30/35.</li><li>The basic attack bonus damage Power ratio has been reduced to 0.1, down from 0.15.</li></ul><li>Landfall (R)</li><ul><li>The range you may cover with this ability has been reduced to 650, down from 760.</li><li>The reactivation range of this ability has been reduced to 550, down from 612.</li><li>The base damage of this ability has been reduced to 150/225/300, down from 200/300/400.</li><li>The Power ratio of this ability has been reduced to 0.6, down from 1.0.</li></ul></ul><h4 style="color: #DAA520;">Closed Beta: Patch 23 (Jan 21, 2014)</h4><ul><li><B>Bolt (Q)</B></li><ul><li>This ability no longer allows Moya to go through walls and will now cause her to slide along them if attempting to go through a wall.</li></ul><li><B>Shock (W)</B></li><ul><li>The Basic Attack Damage bonus granted by activating this ability has been changed to 15/20/25/30/35, from 10/18/26/34/42.</li></ul><li><B>Recharge (E)</B></li><ul><li>The Basic Attack Damage bonus granted by activating this ability has been changed to 15/20/25/30/35, from 10/18/26/34/42.</li><li>The damage boost when using Bolt (Q) while using this ability has been reduced to 35/50/65/80/95, down from 35/55/75/95/115.</li><li>The damage boost power ratio when using Bolt (Q) while this ability is active has been reduced to 0.3, down from 0.35.</li></ul><li><B>Landfall (R)</B></li><ul><li>The base damage of this ability has been reduced to 200/300/400, down from 250/350/450.</li></ul></ul><h4 style="color: #DAA520;">Closed Beta: Patch 22 (Jan 14, 2014)</h4><ul><li><B>Landfall (R)</B></li><ul><li>Changed the targeting silhouette to reflect the narrower hit detection correctly.</li></ul></ul><h4 style="color: #DAA520;">Closed Beta: Patch 20 (December 11, 2013)</h4><ul><li><B>Celerity - Passive</B></li><ul><li>This passive ability now grants bonus Attack Speed instead of Haste. The amount of Attack Speed gained is the same as if it still gave Haste, but now will no longer grant CDR and Move Speed now that it no longer gives Haste.</li></ul><li><b>Landfall (R)</b></li><ul><li>The width of this ability has been decreased to 75, down from 115.</li></ul></ul><h4 style="color: #DAA520;">Closed Beta: Patch 18 (November 21, 2013)</h4><ul><li><B>Bolt (Q)</B></li><ul><li>This ability is now flagged as a targeted line style ability, allowing non smart cast users to more accurately indicate the distance they will travel.</li></ul></ul><h4 style="color: #DAA520;">Closed Beta: Patch 16 (Oct 31, 2013)</h4><ul><li>Fixed a bug that was causing Moya's Shock (W) to not correctly slow affected Shapers struck by the projectiles spawned from the item Fate's passive ability.</li></ul><h4 style="color: #DAA520;">Closed Beta: Patch 13 (October 13, 2013)</h4><ul><li><B>Passive - Celerity</B></li><ul><li>The bonus haste per point of energy missing that this passive ability grants has been reduced to a maximum of 34 bonus Haste at level 1 to 110 bonus haste at level 20, down from a maximum of 35 bonus hate at level 1 to 130 bonus haste at level 20.</li></ul><li><B>Recharge (E)</B></li><ul><li>The flat healing on basic attack from this ability has been reduced to 5/10/15/20/25, down from 8/14/20/26/32.</li></ul></ul><h4 style="color: #DAA520;">Closed Beta: Patch 11 (August 29, 2013)</h4><ul><li><B>Landfall (R)</B></li><ul><li>Fixed a bug that was causing users be unable to reactivate this ability and choose a target location to drop to at the end of the duration.</li><li>Fixed a bug that allowed Shapers to attack a target who was suppressed by this ability.</li></ul></ul><h4 style="color: #DAA520;">Closed Beta: Patch 10 (August 23, 2013)</h4><ul><li><B>Shock (W)</B></li><ul><li>The slow that this ability applies will now affect all targets hit by the item Fate's additional projectiles.</li></ul><li><B>Recharge (E)</B></li><ul><li>The healing granted by this ability will now apply from all targets hit by the item Fate's additional projectiles.</li></ul></ul><h4 style="color: #DAA520;">Closed Beta: Patch 7 (August 02, 2013)</h4><ul><li>Basic attack range increased to 130, up from 95.</li><li><B>Bolt (Q)</B></li><ul><li>The cooldown of this ability has been increased to 5.5/5/4.5/4/3.5, up from 3.5 at all ranks.</li></ul></ul><h4 style="color: #DAA520;">Closed Beta: Patch 5 (July 18, 2013)</h4><ul><li><B>Recharge (E)</B></li><ul><li>The on-hit heal on this ability no longer heals when attacking Bindings or the Guardian.</li></ul><li><B>Landfall (R)</B></li><ul><li>The cooldown of this ability has been increased to 150/140/130 seconds, up from 140/120/100 seconds.</li></ul></ul><h4 style="color: #DAA520;">Closed Beta: Patch 3 (June 21, 2013)</h4><ul><li><B>Shock (W)</B></li><ul><li>Basic attack slow duration has been increased to 1.5 seconds, up from 1. Basic attack slow percentage has been adjusted to 20/25/30/35/40%, from 18/24/30/36/42%. Basic attack damage bonus increased to 10/20/30/40/50, up from 10/18/26/34/42.</li></ul><li><B>Recharge (E)</B></li><ul><li>This ability's passive stacks will now correctly disappear when Varian is killed.</li></ul></ul><h4 style="color: #DAA520;">Closed Beta: Patch 2 (June 13, 2013)</h4><ul><li>Updated visuals on Moya's Eel.</li><li><B>Wrath (R)</B></li><ul><li>Fixed an issue where Moya's abilities were not properly displaying lighting effects when activated.</li></ul></ul><h4 style="color: #DAA520;">Closed Beta: Patch 1 (June 06, 2013)</h4><ul><li><B>General</B><ul><li>Moya's Basic Attack Animation timing has been greatly reduced to feel more responsive.</li></ul></li><li><B>Landfall (R)</B><ul><li>Increased the window for reactivating Landfall to 2 seconds, up from 1.5 seconds and added a buff that indicates the time the player has to reactivate of this ability.</li></ul></li><li><B>Landfall (R)</B><ul><li>The blue ring that indicates the reactivation area of this ability will now automatically disappear after 2 seconds, instead of 3.</li></ul></li></ul>